minRewardsImpact.desc: the minimum impact score to qualify for daily disbursement

akitaAppList.desc: the list of akita contract ids

pluginAppList.desc: the list of plugin contract ids

otherAppList.desc: the list of other contract ids we use

krbyPercentage.desc:
The percentage of total rewards allocated to krby expressed in the hundreds
eg. 3% is 300, 12.75% is 1275

removePluginProposalSettings.desc: proposal settings for removing a plugin

newEscrowProposalSettings.desc: proposal settings for creating a new escrow

toggleEscrowLockProposalSettings.desc: proposal settings for toggling an escrow lock

plugins.desc: Plugins that add functionality to the controlledAddress and the account that has permission to use it.

receiveEscrows.desc: escrow accounts for services to payback revenue to the DAO

payoutEscrows.desc: escrow accounts meant to payout recipients
